== Overview ==
The Hydron Core Mk. II is designed for those who require vast amounts of reserve power and less need for immediate recharging.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Hydron Core Mk. II Reactor can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.

